  "detailed_description": "<h1>MoneyFalls RTX</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >MoneyFalls RTX is here, Realtime Reflections, Shadows and Global Illumination to light those coins up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nvidia Gpu required.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DirectX 12.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nvidia 4060 base model.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recommended to lower screen resolution in base models.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To play it, Go to the Betas tab in the properties of the game and select \"nvidia - Version RTX\" as the beta to play.  </p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>MoneyFalls is a coin pusher simulator with  accurate physics and stunning graphics with many added items and gadgets that makes the game more challenging.</strong><br><br>MoneyFalls is a growing game that is been updated and will grow with many more addons and new machines, Also there is a VR version that needs just to be updated, Next  RTX and other goodies, Updates will be Free as the game grows.<br><br>Many gadgets and mini games also other machines and challenges to discover yourself.(No images included)<br><br>Top 5 on the world<br><br>Added in version 1.2<br><br>4 More new machines.<br><br>1 New Coin Pusher with new challenges..",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>MoneyFalls is a coin pusher simulator with  accurate physics and stunning graphics with many added items and gadgets that makes the game more challenging.</strong><br><br>MoneyFalls is a growing game that is been updated and will grow with many more addons and new machines, Also there is a VR version that needs just to be updated, Next  RTX and other goodies, Updates will be Free as the game grows.<br><br>Many gadgets and mini games also other machines and challenges to discover yourself.(No images included)<br><br>Top 5 on the world<br><br>Added in version 1.2<br><br>4 More new machines.<br><br>1 New Coin Pusher with new challenges..",
